Maintainer: Bojian Zhu <bjzhu999@gmail.com>
Description: Unlock the power of large-scale geospatial analysis, 
    quickly generate high-resolution kernel density visualizations, 
    supporting advanced analysis tasks such as bandwidth-tuning and spatiotemporal analysis. 
    No matter how large your dataset, our library delivers efficient and accurate results. 
